lead_paragraph: Brice Johnson had 14 points and 10 rebounds to help No. 8 North Carolina beat Syracuse 75-70 on Monday night in its home finale.

headline.print_headline: Johnson, No. 8 North Carolina Hold Off Syracuse 75-70
